      <title>纽约联储调查发现美国人正在为更高的住房成本做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/ny-fed-survey-finds-americans-bracing-higher-housing-costs-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行周一表示，由于租房者越来越预期自己永远买不起房子，美国人再次面临新一轮住房成本上涨的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/ny-fed-survey-finds-americans-bracing-higher-housing-costs-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 15:12:55 GMT</pubDate>
